Cattle / - / 18 / - / 18 / -
Sheep and/or goats / - / 90 / - / 90 / -

Outbreak 2: Sain hoot, Bayanjargalan soum, Tuv
Date of start of the outbreak: 19 Nov 2010
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: farm
Affected animals:
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Cattle / - / 19 / - / 19 / -
Sheep and/or goats / - / 55 / - / 55 / -

Outbreak 3: Muu Khoot, Sumber soum, Govi-Sumber
Date of start of the outbreak: 19 Nov 2010
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: farm
Affected animals
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Cattle / - / 22 / - / 22 / -
